        """

        """

        # Get AT/GC/N counts
        at = sum(map(sequence.count, ["A", "T"]))
        gc = sum(map(sequence.count, ["G", "C"]))
        n = length - (at + gc)

        at_prop = at / length
        gc_prop = gc / length
        n_prop = n / length

summarize: def accuracy(output, target, topk=(1,)):
    """"""

    """

    low, high = a % n, n
    while low > 1:
